    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs great and has been well-loved, with just the usual minor wear you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s totally ready for your next road trip or even just the daily commute. I\u2019d love for someone to get as much joy out of it as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit showcases exceptional throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally shimmed for optimal timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a robust limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry is maintained by a set of refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the communicative feedback expected of this chassis. While the exterior displays a light patina of road use, the internal mechanical components\u2014including the rod bearings and cooling system\u2014have been strictly monitored, making this a turn-key performance machine for the enthusiast driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. Runs well.",
      "price": 34500.0,
