      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this professionally maintained vehicle, which demonstrates a commendable standard of mechanical reliability and aesthetic preservation. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for performance and safety. Featuring a clean history and well-preserved interior appointments, this vehicle represents a premier choice for the pragmatic buyer seeking a sophisticated balance of utility and enduring quality. This is an exceptional acquisition opportunity for those who demand excellence and value in equal measure.",
