    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
