    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is this 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a driver-focused example featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This unit boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent mechanical overhaul includes a valve adjustment, rod bearing replacement, and a refreshed cooling system to ensure thermal efficiency under load. The suspension utilizes Bilstein B6 dampers and polyurethane bushings for enhanced lateral stability. While the aesthetics reflect its mileage, the drivetrain remains in peak operational harmony, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery characteristic of the M-division's naturally aspirated era.",
